D&h=9260fab6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://finance.ifeng.com/c/7xgJ6zkPtKF</a><br />\n<br />\n======<br />\n黃channel撐得好辛苦，可以幫手subscribe嗎？<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/XRU8AB0lAxk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FXRU8AB0lAxk&d=Q4XCoHks6IcJcnuFSE4RTUYD92OErucUe%2F0sHRi%2FZkY%3D&h=86abdc79\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/XRU8AB0lAxk</a><br />\n<br />\nTwitter：<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/SomethinkMore/status/1277265956385873920?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSomethinkMore%2Fstatus%2F1277265956385873920%3Fs%3D20&d=Q4XCoHks6IcJcnuFSE4RTUYD92OErucUe%2F0sHRi%2FZkY%3D&h=4f85a1b8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSomethinkMore%2Fstatus%2F1277265956385873920%3Fs%3D20&h=a9514d1f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/SomethinkMore/status/1277265956385873920?s=20</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T10:08:23.000Z","msg":"大家互相鬥卸膊，到最後盤數搞唔店就和味囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dde4a14f08386910fe09dd92e83e9b564b06418b","tid":2084410,"uid":276655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T10:11:00.000Z","msg":"石頭很忙"},{"pid":"a5b32309b10aa1d0c81efb4fe8735b5da0c3e1ef","tid":2084410,"uid":42119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T10:14:06.000Z","msg":"等假交換<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69a955557aae0e067445e3d2de04c9236612bffe","tid":2084410,"uid":110313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T10:14:20.000Z","msg":"邊間audit firm 做aduit<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2799d73fe93098bc79622285c03449aa55f05bdb","tid":2084410,"uid":172627